gt;</content><link href="https://www.discuss.com.hk/viewthread.php?tid=32002694&amp;extra=page%3D1%26amp%3Bfilter%3D0%26amp%3Borderby%3Ddateline%26amp%3Bascdesc%3DDESC&amp;tr_h=17767440176896adde9e04f6_73357863"/><published>2025-08-09T08:56:20+08:00</published></entry><entry><id>1a3c8cf45d836981a39f1052e9669523</id><title>租樓的好處 Aug2025</title><updated>2025-08-09T08:56:59+08:00</updated><author><name>smart004</name></author><content type="html">&lt;p&gt;Published on: 2025-08-09T08:56:59+0800&lt;/p&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;div class="postmessage-content t_msgfont" id="postmessage_573532234"&gt;&lt;!-- google_ad_section_start --&gt;&lt;span id="postorig_573532234"&gt;本討論區好多窮業主&lt;br&gt;日日供負資產&lt;br/&gt;以為十年二十年就會好 , 只要一失業佢哋就要上天台&lt;br/&gt;更可惜, 佢地數學未達中學程度&lt;br/&gt;吾識計數&lt;br/&gt;Compound interest&lt;br/&gt;Net present value, etc&lt;br/&gt;&lt;br/&gt;&lt;br/&gt;然後就大聲講話: 租是洗費&lt;br/&gt;&lt;span style="font-size:22px;"&gt;😁&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="font-size:22px;"&gt;😁&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="font-size:22px;"&gt;😁&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="font-size:22px;"&gt;😁&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br/&gt;ps.但係佢哋從來唔敢將所有買樓成本&lt;br/&gt;供樓成本計清楚&lt;/br&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br/&gt;&lt;br/&gt;&lt;br/&gt; &lt;!-- google_ad_section_end --&gt;&lt;/div&gt;</content><link href="https://www.discuss.com.hk/viewthread.php?tid=32002696&amp;extra=page%3D1%26amp%3Bfilter%3D0%26amp%3Borderby%3Ddateline%26amp%3Bascdesc%3DDESC&amp;tr_h=17767440176896adde9e04f6_73357863"/><published>2025-08-09T08:56:59+08:00</published></entry><entry><id>99c564a83b532be3df95682e7a70c35a</id><title>港島連巨型露台私宅 每呎僅9600元「新界價」推拍</title><updated>2025-08-09T09:52:05+08:00</updated><author><name>叔叔要不要</name></author><content type="html">&lt;p&gt;Published on: 2025-08-09T09:52:05+0800&lt;/p&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;div class="postmessage-content t_msgfont" id="postmessage_573532705"&gt;&lt;!-- google_ad_section_start --&gt;&lt;span id="postorig_573532705"&gt;忠誠拍賣將於下周三(13日)推拍大坑道勤屋中層28號單位，實用面積約1,204方呎，設大型露台，由遺產承辦人推出拍賣，是次開價1,160萬元，呎價僅約9,635元。&lt;br&gt;&lt;br/&gt;該行指出，單位銀行估價約1,460萬元，呎價達約12,126元，現時開價低約20.5%。&lt;br/&gt;&lt;br/&gt;&lt;br/&gt;&lt;br/&gt;原文網址：港島連巨型露台私宅每呎僅9600元「新界價」推拍 | on.cc東網 | 產經 &lt;a class="bburl" href="https://r.discuss.com.hk/link.php?url=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Ffinance%2F20250808%2Fmobile%2Fbkn-20250808221125033-0808_00842_001.html%3Fkeywordid%3D4028828d7471d2a50174ba053e176f16%26keywordname%3D%25E5%259C%25B0%25E7%2594%25A2&amp;amp;platform=&amp;amp;uhash=af1b74ef0467ebbcd096819f9ce59cc6&amp;amp;fid=110" target="_blank"&gt;https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/fina ... &amp;amp;amp;keywordname=地產&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/br&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br/&gt;&lt;br/&gt;&lt;br/&gt; &lt;!-- google_ad_section_end --&gt;&lt;/div&gt;</content><link href="https://www.discuss.com.hk/viewthread.php?tid=32002723&amp;extra=page%3D1%26amp%3Bfilter%3D0%26amp%3Borderby%3Ddateline%26amp%3Bascdesc%3DDESC&amp;tr_h=17767440176896adde9e04f6_73357863"/><published>2025-08-09T09:52:05+08:00</published></entry><entry><id>c718d83200fd256224963787cf554f58</id><title>業主移民！蝕賣沙田有裝修特色戶 單位5年貶近20%</title><updated>2025-08-09T09:52:47+08:00</updated><author><name>叔叔要不要</name></author><content type="html">&lt;p&gt;Published on: 2025-08-09T09:52:47+0800&lt;/p&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;div class="postmessage-content t_msgfont" id="postmessage_573532716"&gt;&lt;!-- google_ad_section_start --&gt;&lt;span id="postorig_573532716"&gt;特色單位樓價向來被看高一線，惟仍難敵整體市況回落。富堡城物業廖志財表示，沙田帝堡城一個頂層特色單位，實用面積約580方呎，為兩房間隔，連天台，有裝修，原業主移民賣樓，7月叫價750萬港元放售。&lt;br&gt;&lt;br/&gt;&lt;br/&gt;他指，上址放盤僅約一個月，減價27萬元，以723萬元成交，呎價約12,466元。原業主於2020年1月以880萬元購入，持貨逾5年半帳面蝕157萬元，樓價下跌約17.8%。資料顯示，大型銀行對上址網上估價約739萬元。&lt;br/&gt;&lt;br/&gt;&lt;br/&gt;&lt;br/&gt;&lt;br/&gt;原文網址：業主移民！蝕賣沙田有裝修特色戶單位5年貶近20% | on.cc東網 | 產經 &lt;a class="bburl" href="https://r.discuss.com.hk/link.php?url=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Ffinance%2F20250808%2Fmobile%2Fbkn-20250808184354018-0808_00842_001.html%3Fkeywordid%3D4028828d7471d2a50174ba053e176f16%26keywordname%3D%25E5%259C%25B0%25E7%2594%25A2&amp;amp;platform=&amp;amp;uhash=439197fa41d9db5399eb1faf221facde&amp;amp;fid=110" target="_blank"&gt;https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/fina ... &amp;amp;amp;keywordname=地產&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/br&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br/&gt;&lt;br/&gt;&lt;br/&gt; &lt;!-- google_ad_section_end --&gt;&lt;/div&gt;</content><link href="https://www.discuss.com.hk/viewthread.php?tid=32002724&amp;extra=page%3D1%26amp%3Bfilter%3D0%26amp%3Borderby%3Ddateline%26amp%3Bascdesc%3DDESC&amp;tr_h=17767440176896adde9e04f6_73357863"/><published>2025-08-09T09:52:47+08:00</published></entry><entry><id>fe868497f9ae540535e3591e439cd89e</id><title>外籍租客455萬入手港島鐵路沿線三房 樓價倒流10年前</title><updated>2025-08-09T09:53:27+08:00</updated><author><name>叔叔要不要</name></author><content type="html">&lt;p&gt;Published on: 2025-08-09T09:53:27+0800&lt;/p&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;div class="postmessage-content t_msgfont" id="postmessage_573532722"&gt;&lt;!-- google_ad_section_start --&gt;&lt;span id="postorig_573532722"&gt;二手樓價回落。中原鄭俊輝表示，柴灣居屋康翠臺5座低層C室，實用面積約646方呎，三房間隔，原先於已補價自由市場叫價470萬港元放售，最終以455萬元成交，累減15萬元，成交呎價約7,043元。&lt;br&gt;&lt;br/&gt;&lt;br/&gt;&lt;br/&gt;原文網址：外籍租客455萬入手港島鐵路沿線三房樓價倒流10年前 | on.cc東網 | 產經 &lt;a class="bburl" href="https://r.discuss.com.hk/link.php?url=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Ffinance%2F20250808%2Fmobile%2Fbkn-20250808140324439-0808_00842_001.html%3Fkeywordid%3D4028828d7471d2a50174ba053e176f16%26keywordname%3D%25E5%259C%25B0%25E7%2594%25A2&amp;amp;platform=&amp;amp;uhash=a4b98f500f32129b0fc58d94e7a3e788&amp;amp;fid=110" target="_blank"&gt;https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/fina ... &amp;amp;amp;keywordname=地產&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/br&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br/&gt;&lt;br/&gt;&lt;br/&gt; &lt;!-- google_ad_section_end --&gt;&lt;/div&gt;</content><link href="https://www.discuss.com.hk/viewthread.php?tid=32002725&amp;extra=page%3D1%26amp%3Bfilter%3D0%26amp%3Borderby%3Ddateline%26amp%3Bascdesc%3DDESC&amp;tr_h=17767440176896adde9e04f6_73357863"/><published>2025-08-09T09:53:27+08:00</published></entry><entry><id>2d956bf7f08562656bc1b5850956389f</id><title>🆘南昌站匯璽海景兩房 較8年前一手價跌22% 貶值3球｜二手樓成交</title><updated>2025-08-09T09:54:14+08:00</updated><author><name>叔叔要不要</name></author><content type="html">&lt;p&gt;Published on: 2025-08-09T09:54:14+0800&lt;/p&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;div class="postmessage-content t_msgfont" id="postmessage_573532738"&gt;&lt;!-- google_ad_section_start --&gt;&lt;span id="postorig_573532738"&gt;&lt;a class="bburl" href="https://r.discuss.com.hk/link.php?url=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.am730.com.hk%2F%25E5%259C%25B0%25E7%2594%25A2%2F%25E5%258D%2597%25E6%2598%258C%25E7%25AB%2599%25E5%258C%25AF%25E7%2592%25BD%25E6%25B5%25B7%25E6%2599%25AF%25E5%2585%25A9%25E6%2588%25BF-%25E8%25BC%25838%25E5%25B9%25B4%25E5%2589%258D%25E4%25B8%2580%25E6%2589%258B%25E5%2583%25B9%25E8%25B7%258C22-%25E8%25B2%25B6%25E5%2580%25BC3%25E7%2590%2583-%25E4%25BA%258C%25E6%2589%258B%25E6%25A8%2593%25E6%2588%2590%25E4%25BA%25A4%2F586910&amp;amp;platform=&amp;amp;uhash=fb39d848246bcf7027b6fb409b376d86&amp;amp;fid=110" target="_blank"&gt;https://www.am730.com.hk/地產/南昌站匯 ... 2-貶值3球-二手樓成交/586910&lt;/a&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;br/&gt;市區海景豪宅鐵路盤錄蝕讓成交。利嘉閣地產新西九龍豪宅奧運站匯璽二行聯席董事徐錦榮表示，南昌站上蓋屋苑匯璽3B座中層A室，單位實用面積449方呎，屬兩房連開放式廚房間隔，外望海景。單位早前獲區內用家垂青，心儀屋苑屬新鴻基品牌，認為物業質素有保證，加上屋苑鄰近高鐵站，方便往返內地工作，遂決定洽購。&lt;br/&gt;&lt;br/&gt;成交呎價逾2.35萬&lt;br/&gt;據悉，單位原以1,068萬元放盤，經議價後以1,058萬元成交，累減10萬元，折合實用呎價23,563元。至於原業主於2017年底以約1,357.8萬元一手購入上址，持貨近8年轉手，帳面需虧損約299.8萬元，期間蝕幅有22%。另外，現時匯璽放盤量約有280個，最低入場費由約510萬元起。&lt;/br&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br/&gt;&lt;br/&gt;&lt;br/&gt; &lt;!-- google_ad_section_end --&gt;&lt;/div&gt;</content><link href="https://www.discuss.com.hk/viewthread.php?tid=32002726&amp;extra=page%3D1%26amp%3Bfilter%3D0%26amp%3Borderby%3Ddateline%26amp%3Bascdesc%3DDESC&amp;tr_h=17767440176896adde9e04f6_73357863"/><published>2025-08-09T09:54:14+08:00</published></entry><entry><id>8154964642fabe470f0da4adae653180</id><title>🆘平過居屋！屯門大興花園兩房蝕讓盤 呎價不足8千 4年大跌31%｜二手樓成交</title><updated>2025-08-09T09:54:58+08:00</updated><author><name>叔叔要不要</name></author><content type="html">&lt;p&gt;Published on: 2025-08-09T09:54:58+0800&lt;/p&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;div class="postmessage-content t_msgfont" id="postmessage_573532744"&gt;&lt;!-- google_ad_section_start --&gt;&lt;span id="postorig_573532744"&gt;&lt;a class="bburl" href="https://r.discuss.com.hk/link.php?url=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.am730.com.hk%2F%25E5%259C%25B0%25E7%2594%25A2%2F%25E5%25B9%25B3%25E9%2581%258E%25E5%25B1%2585%25E5%25B1%258B-%25E5%25B1%25AF%25E9%2596%2580%25E5%25A4%25A7%25E8%2588%2588%25E8%258A%25B1%25E5%259C%2592%25E5%2585%25A9%25E6%2588%25BF%25E8%259D%2595%25E8%25AE%2593%25E7%259B%25A4-%25E5%2591%258E%25E5%2583%25B9%25E4%25B8%258D%25E8%25B6%25B38%25E5%258D%2583-4%25E5%25B9%25B4%25E5%25A4%25A7%25E8%25B7%258C31-%25E4%25BA%258C%25E6%2589%258B%25E6%25A8%2593%25E6%2588%2590%25E4%25BA%25A4%2F586831&amp;amp;platform=&amp;amp;uhash=86ec9ac6700fce1a42f764a7add216cc&amp;amp;fid=110" target="_blank"&gt;https://www.am730.com.hk/地產/平過居屋 ... 4年大跌31-二手樓成交/586831&lt;/a&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;br/&gt;屯門上車屋苑大興花園一夥兩房低層單位，原業主持貨4年，忍痛止蝕「跳船」，大幅蝕31%沽貨，成交呎價不足8,000元，平過居屋。中原地產屯門瓏門二期第二分行高級分區營業經理鍾宏遠表示，近月息口顯著回落，「供平過租」推動不少租客入市置業。分行新近促成大興花園2期3座低層H室成交，單位實用面積419方呎，採兩房間隔，原本叫價350萬元，經議價後減價17萬元，以333萬元成交，平均實用呎價7,947元。&lt;br/&gt;&lt;br/&gt;租客唔想捱貴租 趁低息上車&lt;br/&gt;鍾宏遠指，新買家為同區租客，見租金一直逆市上升，現時供樓平過租樓的情況明顯，加上美國將會減息，預計低息環境持續，遂轉租為買，入市上車。原業主則於2021年8月以480萬元購入上述單位，持貨約4年，現帳面損手147萬元，期內貶值約31%。&lt;/br&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br/&gt;&lt;br/&gt;&lt;br/&gt; &lt;!-- google_ad_section_end --&gt;&lt;/div&gt;</content><link href="https://www.discuss.com.hk/viewthread.php?tid=32002727&amp;extra=page%3D1%26amp%3Bfilter%3D0%26amp%3Borderby%3Ddateline%26amp%3Bascdesc%3DDESC&amp;tr_h=17767440176896adde9e04f6_73357863"/><published>2025-08-09T09:54:58+08:00</published></entry></feed>